---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Reduce Photo Size"
  description="Read the Terms of Service of Reduce Photo Size. Learn about our client-side image resizing and formatting tool rules, usage policies, and disclaimers."
>
  <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 py-20 lg:py-28 space-y-10 transition-all duration-150">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="text-[13px] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] flex items-center gap-2">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] transition-colors">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] font-medium">Terms of Service</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-[36px] font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[14px] text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        Last updated: June 2026 • Version 1.0
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Clause (Aesthetic Highlight Box) -->
    <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-[8px] bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] p-6 space-y-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold text-[14px] uppercase tracking-wider">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
        </svg>
        Fair Use & Privacy Guarantee
      </div>
      <p class="text-[14px] text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        Reduce Photo Size is a 100% free, static client-side web utility provided without warranty. No account setup or registration is required, and all processing is strictly executed on your browser.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Detailed Terms -->
    <div class="space-y-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using Reduce Photo Size, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must refrain from using the tools.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>
          Reduce Photo Size provides browser-based utilities to help users format, resize, crop, and convert image files (photographs and signatures) to comply with official guidelines for recruitment and admission portals. All computations, image processing, and formatting happen locally on your computer or device.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">3. User Responsibility & Disclaimers</h2>
        <p>
          While we make every effort to keep target specifications (dimensions, file size ranges, formats) up-to-date with official portal requirements, rules may change without notice. 
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5 text-[14px]">
          <li>You are solely responsible for verifying that the output file meets the requirements of the specific portal you are submitting to.</li>
          <li>We do not warrant or guarantee that the generated images will be accepted by any third-party registration system.</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for any rejection of applications, forms, or exams due to file formatting discrepancies.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">4. Permitted and Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes related to preparing documents for registration portals. You may not attempt to reverse engineer the code, flood or scrape pages, or use local processing scripts to process mass batches of files maliciously.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          Reduce Photo Size is built using open-source packages. All code and scripts executing the resizing logic are licensed under open, public terms. You are free to inspect, download, and audit our code directly from our GitHub repository.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section class="space-y-3 border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] pt-8">
        <h2 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] italic">
          THE UTILITY IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. REDUCE PHOTO SIZE DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, INCLUDING MERCHANTABILITY, ACCURACY, AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
